{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that's-- that-- that was the rule there, you know, that you can go to school until you are seven.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So seven years old I entered first elementary school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, by the time in the '30s that I went to the gymnasium, the Nazis, you know, was growing, see?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it affected.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why did it affect?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I have to tell you what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I lived in northern part of Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And northern part of Transylvania at the time that I got to school, even first elementary school, belonged to Romania.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And actually, the whole Transylvania belonged to Romania.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my husband is from southern part of Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, in the southern part of Transylvania, the Jewish people were taken to forced labor camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and but in northern part of Transylvania, you know, then it became Hungary in 1940.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "See, in 1940 were very hard times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But even before that, the all the Jews from northern part of Transylvania, which was Hungary in 1944, were taken out to the German concentration camps, the sick people, everyone.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no-- there was no Jew left in-- in-- except some people who maybe who were in hiding, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they pulled them out from the hospitals, from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, what happened, that after the end of First World War in 1920 was signed a treaty, which was called a Trianon Treaty.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after this treaty, naturally, Hungary was practically, parts of Hungary were parceled out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were parceled out to Czechoslovakia, to-- and and whole Transylvania, you know, went to Romania.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Hungarians resented that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, suddenly, the whole of Transylvania in 1920 became Romania.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, when I started school, I had to go to Romanian schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
